desc: Sweet Gisele offers high-quality, cutting-edge apparel, novelty mugs and souvenirs. Based out of New York, we’re proud to be made in the USA manufacturers. We digitally print our original designs on 100% of our products including t-shirts, hoodies, and more, while specializing in all-over-print and stone embellishment.
